              {
                "type": "dialogue",
                "text": "Let's look closer at the Cats category. Scale of 1 uses 8 symbols. Scale of 2 uses only 4 symbols, half as many. When each symbol represents more pets, you need fewer symbols to show the same data. Scale of 2 uses fewer symbols.",
